2) and |Vcb Yb| = |Yc| at the grand unified theory scale.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2009 19:32:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 Jan 2010 23:23:59 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 17 Jan 2010 04:33:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
