 another. We must, therefore,\nacknowledge the strong possibility that the atmosphere is variable, both in its\nenergy redistribution state and in the chemical abundances.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2009 20:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Jan 2010 20:32:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
